    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-700 mb-8">Hi! I'm Kashish</h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-10 font-medium">
                Cat lover, developer, and the creator of Whisker Way
            </p>
            <!-- Social Media & Portfolio Links -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kashish-verma-b57b052a6/" 
                   class="bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transform hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100">
                    <i class="fas fa-briefcase text-lg"></i>
                    <span class="font-semibold">LinkedIn</span>
                </a>

                <a href="https://www.kashishverma.com" 
                   class="bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transform hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100">
                    <i class="fas fa-briefcase text-lg"></i>
                    <span class="font-semibold">Portfolio</span>
                </a>

                <a href="https://github.com/KashishV999" 
                   class="bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transform hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100">
                    <i class="fas fa-briefcase text-lg"></i>
                    <span class="font-semibold">Github</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- About Section -->
<div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Left Column (Image) -->
        <div class="flex justify-center">
            <img class="w-68 rounded-2xl shadow-md" src="https://www.elifnotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/benefits-of-reading-fiction.webp" alt="Hiking in nature" />
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column (About Me) -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-700 mb-4">The Heart Behind Whisker Haven</h2>
                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-teal-300 rounded"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                <p class="text-lg">
                    My love for cats was the biggest inspiration behind creating 
                    <span class="font-semibold text-teal-600">Whisker Haven</span>. 
                    I wanted to build something that truly reflects what I care about and what's closer to my heart.
                </p>
                
                <p class="text-lg">
                    I'm currently expanding my tech toolkit, diving into new technologies, and even exploring 
                    LLMs and LangGraph architecture
                    to eventually integrate AI. My goal is to make this site smart enough to help every cat find their perfect home.
                </p>
                
                <p class="text-lg">
                    When I'm not coding, you'll find me watching dramatic Korean or Turkish dramas 
                    (the more emotional chaos, the better!), reading fictional books, or cooking something delicious in the kitchen.
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg italic text-teal-700 bg-teal-50 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-teal-200">
                    "Honestly, all you need is a good meal, some rain outside, a good drama playing, 
                    and a cat curled up beside you, that's what home feels like to me."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>